verbose_text: Significant changes were observed in levels of nitrate at all times, with lower values in the end of the season (September 2009 : 32.8 mg kg -1 +/- 7.08; October 2010 : 24.2 mg kg -1 +/- 2.98) and higher at the beginning (April 2009 : 75.6 mg kg -1 +/- 12.5; April 2010 : 56.4 mg kg -1 +/- 5.63).
